    "patch_code": "public static boolean isJSIdentifier(String s) {\n  int length = s.length();\n\n  if (length == 0 ||\n     Character.isUpperCase(s.charAt(0)) || \n     Character.isLowerCase(s.charAt(0)) ||\n     s.charAt(0) == '\\n' || s.charAt(0)=='\\r'||\n     s.charAt(0)=='\\t' ) {\n     return false;\n  }\n\n  for (int i = 1; i < length; i++) {\n   if (!Character.isLetterOrDigit(s.charAt(i))&&\n       s.charAt(i)!='\\n' && s.charAt(i)!='\\r'&&\n       s.charAt(i)!='\\t')\n  {\n      return false;\n    }\n  }\n \n  return true;\n}",
